WEBVTT

00:04:59.247 --> 00:05:00.888
according to where they are.

00:05:01.685 --> 00:05:04.170
If you find yourself
in a bad neighborhood,

00:05:04.194 --> 00:05:05.449
you turn it up.

00:05:05.878 --> 00:05:07.527
Out to dinner with family?

00:05:07.551 --> 00:05:09.479
You turn it way down.

00:05:09.975 --> 00:05:12.747
We train veterans to be fiercely rational,

00:05:13.271 --> 00:05:16.825
to systematically gauge
the actual statistical probability

00:05:16.849 --> 00:05:20.657
of encountering, say, an IED
here in peacetime America.

00:05:21.460 --> 00:05:25.724
With enough practice,
those recalibrations stick.

00:05:27.193 --> 00:05:29.507
The next of these treatments
is exposure therapy,

00:05:29.531 --> 00:05:31.958
and this is a kind of field training,